snippet.title: Lemmings: Arcade Prototype (1991)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on an Arcade System in 1991. This game never made it past the arcade field test stage.
Developed by T R Development Inc and published by Data East.

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
